    self.travel_routes: ANRs travel routes layer, needs to be downloaded
    self.rei_segments: ANRs forest road segments for collecting road erosion inventory data, needs to be downloaded 
    self.joined_routes: the combined layer with travel routes and 
    self.clean_routes: an intermediate step in clean(); routes within state lands 
    self.lr_routes: Routes to be dynamically segmented 
    self.events: event table of dymanic segmentation
    self.public: the final, public facing layer 

    Functions:
    __init__() - initializes the class
    clean() - merges travel routes and rei forest road segments 
    add_id() - create a numeric id for each road 
